org.gservlet

Class ContainerInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gservlet.ContainerInitializer

  • public class ContainerInitializer
extends java.lang.Object
    The ContainerInitializer class manages the registration and the reloading of a servlet, filter or listener into the web container.
